       VALORE-OLD-RIGA.
      * <TOTEM:PARA. VALORE-OLD-RIGA>
           if vecchio
              inquire form1-gd-1(riga, 1) cell-data tav-codice
              read ttipoavv               no lock
              move tav-rec                to old-tav-rec
           else
              initialize old-tav-rec replacing numeric data by zeroes
                                          alphanumeric data by spaces
           end-if 
           .
      * <TOTEM:END>

       VALORIZZA-DATI-COMUNI.
      * <TOTEM:PARA. VALORIZZA-DATI-COMUNI>
      * SE NON HO VALORIZZATO I CAMPI DI CREAZIONE LI VALORIZZO
           if tav-data-creazione = zero
              accept tav-data-creazione from century-date
           end-if.
           if tav-ora-creazione = zero
              accept tav-ora-creazione from time
           end-if.
           if tav-utente-creazione = space
              move user-codi to tav-utente-creazione
           end-if.

           accept tav-data-ultima-modifica from century-date.
           accept tav-ora-ultima-modifica from time.
           move user-codi to tav-utente-ultima-modifica 
           .
      * <TOTEM:END>

       CAMBIA-BITMAP.
      * <TOTEM:PARA. CAMBIA-BITMAP>
      *     inquire form1-gd-1(riga, 3), 
      *             hidden-data = num-bitmap

      *     if num-bitmap = 1
      *        move 2 to num-bitmap
      *     else
      *        move 1 to num-bitmap
      *     end-if
      *   
      *     modify form1-gd-1(riga, 3), bitmap-number = num-bitmap
      *                                 hidden-data = num-bitmap.
           perform SETTA-BMP

           perform VALORE-RIGA
           set NoSalvato to true
           perform SALVA
           .
      * <TOTEM:END>

       SETTA-BMP.
      * <TOTEM:PARA. SETTA-BMP>
           evaluate true
           when tav-no-auto
                move 1 to num-bitmap
                move 2 to num-bitmap-promo
                move 2 to num-bitmap-banner-t
                move 2 to num-bitmap-banner-g
           when tav-promo
                move 2 to num-bitmap
                move 1 to num-bitmap-promo
                move 2 to num-bitmap-banner-t
                move 2 to num-bitmap-banner-g
           when tav-banner-trad
                move 2 to num-bitmap
                move 2 to num-bitmap-promo
                move 1 to num-bitmap-banner-t
                move 2 to num-bitmap-banner-g
           when tav-banner-gdo
                move 2 to num-bitmap
                move 2 to num-bitmap-promo 
                move 2 to num-bitmap-banner-t
                move 1 to num-bitmap-banner-g
           end-evaluate

           modify form1-gd-1(riga, 3), 
                             bitmap-number = num-bitmap
                             bitmap conferma-bmp
                             bitmap-width 19
           modify form1-gd-1(riga, 4), 
                             bitmap-number = num-bitmap-promo
                             bitmap conferma-bmp
                             bitmap-width 19
           modify form1-gd-1(riga, 5), 
                             bitmap-number = num-bitmap-banner-t
                             bitmap conferma-bmp
                             bitmap-width 19
           modify form1-gd-1(riga, 6),
                             bitmap-number = num-bitmap-banner-g
                             bitmap conferma-bmp
                             bitmap-width 19

           modify form1-gd-1(riga, 1), hidden-data tav-automatismi
           .
